name: Part of The Plan
description:
The artwork story :

Nobody panics when things go ‘according to plan.’ 
Even if the plan is horrifying! If, tomorrow, 
I tell the press that, like, a gang banger will 
get shot or a truckload of soldiers will be blown up, 
nobody panics, because it’s all part of the plan.

digital painting 2480 x 2750 px
